WEBVTT

00:17.000 --> 00:23.120
FUNERAL CORTEGE OF HE JINGYUAN
LOYAL AND UPRIGHT GENERAL OF DAYIN

00:23.200 --> 00:25.920
MEMORIAL OFFERING

00:26.000 --> 00:27.760
SPIRIT TABLET OF HE JINGYUAN
GOVERNOR OF JIZHOU

00:35.040 --> 00:37.080
-General He, may you rest in peace.
-General He, may you rest in peace.

00:42.440 --> 00:44.280
General He, may your spirit rest in peace.

01:02.240 --> 01:03.200
General He…

01:05.360 --> 01:06.560
rest in peace.

01:18.040 --> 01:19.680
WEI QILIN, CRIMINAL OF DAYIN

01:22.560 --> 01:23.720
Wei Qilin!

01:24.400 --> 01:26.160
You treacherous traitor!

01:27.600 --> 01:30.440
He tried to run. Served him right
when he went over the cliff

01:30.520 --> 01:31.360
with his whole family!

01:31.440 --> 01:32.880
He deserved it!

01:32.960 --> 01:34.840
And now, even General He
has died on the battlefield,

01:34.920 --> 01:36.720
-all because of that traitor!
-Beat him!

01:36.800 --> 01:38.120
-Beat that traitor!
-Beat him!

01:40.040 --> 01:42.720
Burn him! Send him below to beg
the two generals' forgiveness.

01:48.200 --> 01:49.040
What are you doing?

01:53.000 --> 01:54.240
You are the woman general

01:54.880 --> 01:56.800
who killed Prince Changxin, are you not?

01:57.680 --> 01:58.640
-Yes.
-That is her.

01:58.720 --> 02:00.720
-Yes, Mrs. Fan.
-It's her.

02:01.240 --> 02:03.720
Mrs. Fan, why did you stop us?

02:03.800 --> 02:04.840
We are burning that traitor!

02:07.080 --> 02:08.320
He is not a traitor.

02:08.400 --> 02:09.400
Mrs. Fan,

02:10.600 --> 02:12.120
we respect you.

02:12.720 --> 02:14.720
A woman who faced death
and slew Prince Changxin.

02:14.800 --> 02:16.280
But why would you defend Wei Qilin,

02:16.360 --> 02:17.520
that traitor?

02:17.600 --> 02:19.160
-I'm--
-Why?

02:19.240 --> 02:20.280
Why are you speaking for him?

02:21.200 --> 02:23.080
He is not. He is not a traitor.

02:23.160 --> 02:25.680
Today is the memorial
for Old General Xie and General He.

02:25.760 --> 02:26.600
What you are doing now

02:26.680 --> 02:29.440
is turning against the entire Jizhou
and Yanzhou army!

02:29.520 --> 02:31.120
Forgive me, Generals.

02:31.640 --> 02:33.560
-But that is not the truth.
-Enough of your nonsense!

02:34.880 --> 02:35.800
That is enough!

02:40.880 --> 02:41.720
-Marquis.
-Marquis.

02:52.200 --> 02:53.080
Let's go.

03:02.520 --> 03:04.240
I haven't paid my respects
to the late General Xie.

03:05.000 --> 03:06.600
I truly came to honor him.

03:07.600 --> 03:08.760
If you defend that traitor,

03:08.840 --> 03:10.880
then you have no right
to bow before General Xie!

03:10.960 --> 03:13.240
The Xie army will never allow it!

03:13.320 --> 03:14.560
-That is right!
-Never!

03:14.640 --> 03:16.240
-Get out!
-Get out!

03:16.320 --> 03:17.160
Form ranks!

03:41.160 --> 03:42.160
Marquis, what are you…

03:42.240 --> 03:46.560
-Marquis, she just--
-Xie army! Yanzhou army! Hear my command!

03:49.520 --> 03:50.360
Kneel.

04:04.200 --> 04:05.200
Generals,

04:06.960 --> 04:07.800
may you rest in peace.

05:47.600 --> 05:52.480
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL ZHU YU
BY TUAN ZI LAI XI ON JJWXC.NET

05:55.240 --> 05:58.280
JIZHOU YAMEN

06:12.200 --> 06:13.120
Changyu.

06:14.920 --> 06:15.800
Are you feeling better?

06:30.120 --> 06:31.520
Commoner Fan Changyu

06:32.480 --> 06:33.360
greets the Marquis.

06:37.240 --> 06:38.240
What did you

06:39.880 --> 06:40.720
just call me?

06:42.720 --> 06:43.920
Marquis.

06:45.440 --> 06:46.800
After all this time,

06:47.560 --> 06:48.760
that is what you settled on?

06:54.080 --> 06:55.680
One word, Marquis…

06:58.120 --> 07:00.000
and suddenly we are strangers.

07:01.200 --> 07:02.760
If the Marquis finds it too distant,

07:03.600 --> 07:05.080
then since we share the same teacher,

07:06.200 --> 07:07.720
you may call me Junior.

07:14.120 --> 07:17.080
Marquis, this is a private residence
and my own chamber.

07:17.680 --> 07:18.800
Please keep your distance.

07:21.640 --> 07:22.960
I think I know

07:24.800 --> 07:25.800
what troubles you.

07:26.720 --> 07:27.880
But you should also know

07:28.400 --> 07:31.040
there is nothing in this world
that could make us strangers.

07:32.240 --> 07:33.520
And what if the matter

07:34.360 --> 07:35.680
were serious enough

07:36.520 --> 07:38.440
to cost you your command
of the Yanzhou army?

07:47.400 --> 07:49.440
Whether I am fit to command an army

07:49.960 --> 07:51.320
depends solely on my own ability.

07:51.400 --> 07:54.160
It has nothing to do
with anyone or anything.

07:54.880 --> 07:55.840
Including you.

07:57.320 --> 07:58.320
So in your view,

07:59.280 --> 08:00.560
everything in this world

08:02.440 --> 08:04.360
is like matters of the army…

08:07.400 --> 08:09.280
and in the end,
you alone decide everything.

08:26.360 --> 08:27.360
It is late.

08:28.280 --> 08:29.520
I still need to tend to my wounds.

08:30.240 --> 08:31.440
Marquis, please leave.

09:00.800 --> 09:02.600
‎JINGHE GATE

09:02.680 --> 09:03.840
Chancellor Wei.

09:04.680 --> 09:05.720
Chancellor Wei.

09:08.440 --> 09:09.360
Grand Tutor.

09:10.320 --> 09:11.680
Would you look at that.

09:11.760 --> 09:13.160
I must be getting old.

09:13.240 --> 09:14.760
My student has a mind of his own now.

09:14.840 --> 09:16.440
I can hardly keep him in line.

09:18.920 --> 09:21.920
This matter concerns
the military command of Jizhou.

09:22.000 --> 09:24.920
We weighed it purely on merit in battle.
There was no personal agenda.

09:25.680 --> 09:28.680
I hope you will not
take offense, Chancellor Wei.

09:30.480 --> 09:32.880
If you truly feel your years
catching up with you,

09:33.400 --> 09:35.680
perhaps you should follow Grand Tutor Tao

09:35.760 --> 09:37.080
and bow out while you're ahead.

09:38.040 --> 09:40.080
To this day, the court, the officials,

09:40.160 --> 09:41.040
even His Majesty,

09:41.920 --> 09:43.680
remember him with nothing but praise.

09:43.760 --> 09:46.760
Far better than clinging
to office well past 70,

09:47.400 --> 09:48.480
throwing around seniority

09:48.560 --> 09:50.640
while unable to keep things in line.

09:55.680 --> 09:57.200
Arrogant, is he?

09:58.120 --> 10:00.080
We lost General He
in the Battle of Lucheng.

10:00.880 --> 10:02.880
In his last words, he strongly recommended

10:02.960 --> 10:04.880
Li Huai'an as the military administrator.

10:05.800 --> 10:08.840
Now that the military command
of Jizhou has slipped from his grasp,

10:08.920 --> 10:11.760
Wei Yan's arrogance
may not last much longer.

10:12.680 --> 10:15.920
As long as Marquis Wu'an continues
to station his army in Lucheng,

10:17.280 --> 10:20.640
control of the troops
will not pass into other hands.

10:20.720 --> 10:21.760
And that

10:22.280 --> 10:24.960
is precisely
where Wei Yan's confidence lies.

10:25.040 --> 10:28.760
HALL OF LETTERS

10:39.880 --> 10:40.720
Mother,

10:40.800 --> 10:44.920
I'll never play the traitor game
with them again.

10:47.200 --> 10:48.640
They are only children.

10:49.360 --> 10:50.360
What do they know?

10:51.320 --> 10:53.720
In this world, how many people

10:53.800 --> 10:56.000
can truly tell loyalty from treachery,

10:56.640 --> 10:57.600
or right from wrong?

11:06.320 --> 11:07.320
Dinner is ready.

11:10.200 --> 11:12.480
All right. Let's go eat.

11:29.640 --> 11:31.760
Father. Mother.

11:32.720 --> 11:34.800
What is all this really about?

11:39.440 --> 11:40.280
Come in.

11:41.720 --> 11:42.680
-Fan!
-Changyu!

11:42.760 --> 11:43.720
Changyu!

11:44.600 --> 11:45.440
Changyu!

11:47.080 --> 11:50.040
-What is all this?
-It has been days now.

11:50.120 --> 11:52.080
-General Fan looks well enough to drink.
-Exactly.

11:52.160 --> 11:54.000
We have been waiting all this time.

11:54.080 --> 11:56.880
We have been eager to come
celebrate with you. Have we not?

11:56.960 --> 11:58.560
General Fan?

11:58.640 --> 11:59.960
You flatter me too much.

12:00.040 --> 12:02.080
In our eyes, you are a true general.

12:02.160 --> 12:04.000
Killing Prince Changxin was no small feat.

12:04.080 --> 12:05.520
Chongzhou will soon be ours.

12:05.600 --> 12:07.600
After that, there'll be
no battles left to fight.

12:07.680 --> 12:08.600
-That is right.
-Exactly.

12:08.680 --> 12:10.000
-Come on. Drink up.
-Come. Changyu.

12:10.080 --> 12:11.280
-Let me fill your cup.
-Fill it up.

12:13.080 --> 12:13.920
Here you go.

12:15.240 --> 12:16.640
Then I thank you all.

12:16.720 --> 12:17.760
Cheers.

12:17.840 --> 12:18.760
-Cheers!
-Drink!

12:19.800 --> 12:20.640
Changyu!

12:24.640 --> 12:25.720
-Drink…
-Changyu.

12:25.800 --> 12:27.240
Lord Li is here asking to see you.

12:28.720 --> 12:29.560
Let him in.

12:30.680 --> 12:32.360
That may not be appropriate.

12:32.440 --> 12:34.400
Changyu, you should go out and see him.

12:35.400 --> 12:38.160
HALL OF LETTERS

12:42.520 --> 12:44.800
Lord Li, what are you doing?

12:45.680 --> 12:46.760
I am ashamed.

12:47.440 --> 12:50.120
I have come today to beg your forgiveness.

12:50.720 --> 12:51.840
My first offense.

12:53.160 --> 12:54.760
When the rebels attacked the city,

12:55.280 --> 12:57.880
you knocked me unconscious
because you feared I might act rashly.

12:58.640 --> 12:59.800
Yet I didn't understand.

13:00.920 --> 13:03.240
Instead, when you were gravely ill,
I spoke harshly to you.

13:04.560 --> 13:05.600
That was unjust.

13:06.760 --> 13:07.920
My second offense.

13:08.600 --> 13:11.000
Our dispute led others
to misunderstand you,

13:11.800 --> 13:13.240
damaging your reputation.

13:13.840 --> 13:15.040
That was discourteous.

13:16.440 --> 13:17.560
So I beg you

13:18.440 --> 13:20.440
to strike me with these brambles.

13:21.880 --> 13:23.680
Otherwise, I won't be able to face you

13:24.720 --> 13:26.720
or General He again.

13:42.880 --> 13:44.280
Please do not dwell on it.

13:44.360 --> 13:45.760
General He treated me well.

13:46.280 --> 13:47.800
I understand the position you were in.

13:48.720 --> 13:50.000
-Please get up.
-I am ashamed.

13:51.120 --> 13:53.160
I thought the northwest had made me wiser.

13:54.600 --> 13:56.120
Yet I'm not as clear-headed as you.

13:56.840 --> 13:58.480
You care too much to think straight.

13:59.760 --> 14:01.040
You're too hard on yourself.

14:03.440 --> 14:06.000
Besides, I was wrong to knock you out.

14:06.600 --> 14:08.200
One fault cancels the other.

14:08.280 --> 14:09.280
We are even now.

14:10.440 --> 14:11.480
Get up.

14:18.360 --> 14:21.400
Counting soldiers, choosing generals,
riding horses, going to war.

14:21.480 --> 14:22.880
I will draw this one.

14:22.960 --> 14:23.920
No peeking.

14:24.000 --> 14:24.840
‎EASTERN OUTSKIRTS OF QINGPING COUNTY

14:24.920 --> 14:26.360
I am drawing the highest card.

14:26.880 --> 14:28.360
Look. Twin Heavens!

14:28.440 --> 14:30.080
I got four pairs of candied hawthorns!

14:30.600 --> 14:33.560
-Look at this. Did I win?
-I won!

14:33.640 --> 14:36.120
-I won!
-It is me. I won!

14:36.200 --> 14:37.920
-Who won this round?
-Mr. Zhao, look.

14:38.000 --> 14:39.200
Tell us who won.

14:39.280 --> 14:41.600
Twin Heavens outrank the great houses.

14:41.680 --> 14:42.920
Bao'er wins this round.

14:44.640 --> 14:45.480
Come on.

14:45.560 --> 14:47.960
-Again.
-Let's play another round.

14:48.040 --> 14:50.320
-All right. That is enough.
-Thunder God! Boom, you're done!

14:50.400 --> 14:52.120
I want the Empress card.

15:06.800 --> 15:07.640
Come here.

15:08.520 --> 15:09.440
Do not run.

15:10.720 --> 15:11.920
It is one of ours.

15:23.000 --> 15:26.120
THATCHED COTTAGE

15:33.880 --> 15:34.760
Bao'er!

15:36.040 --> 15:37.040
Ning!

15:41.320 --> 15:42.920
Pretty Lady!

15:49.160 --> 15:51.200
Mother, you are finally back!

15:51.880 --> 15:53.120
I missed you so much!

15:55.000 --> 15:56.720
I missed you too.

15:59.200 --> 16:00.200
Ms. Yu.

16:00.760 --> 16:02.280
You are back.

16:11.320 --> 16:14.320
Changyu asked General Xie Qi
to escort me home.

16:14.920 --> 16:16.880
She said no one in Lin'an
is to be left behind.

16:18.080 --> 16:18.960
And I am

16:20.240 --> 16:21.400
one of you.

16:21.920 --> 16:23.880
Changyu really is something.

16:24.400 --> 16:27.240
First she sent me,
Changning, and Bao'er home.

16:27.920 --> 16:31.080
-Now she has brought back another.
-It is good you are back.

16:31.160 --> 16:34.320
-That's one missing piece home.
-Yes, indeed.

16:39.560 --> 16:41.000
TEN DAYS LATER

16:41.080 --> 16:42.200
JIZHOU PREFECTURAL OFFICE

17:14.560 --> 17:15.720
Why are you still here?

17:16.240 --> 17:18.560
-What?
-Come on.

17:35.680 --> 17:36.520
Speak.

17:36.600 --> 17:39.160
Marquis Wu'an sent word
that military matters are pressing.

17:39.240 --> 17:40.920
He cannot attend.
He said not to wait for him.

17:44.440 --> 17:46.760
Eunuch, if the decree
is not announced soon,

17:46.840 --> 17:48.520
we will miss the auspicious hour.

17:54.160 --> 17:56.200
Very well. We will wait no longer.

17:57.240 --> 17:58.440
Then,

18:00.320 --> 18:02.160
we will announce the first two decrees.

18:02.240 --> 18:05.000
HALL OF LETTERS

18:05.080 --> 18:06.880
Where are we going? I have meat stewing.

18:06.960 --> 18:07.840
Come on.

18:18.320 --> 18:20.120
-Where were you?
-Everyone is here.

18:20.200 --> 18:21.080
Finally.

18:30.880 --> 18:32.960
-How long does it take to read the decree?
-Shh!

18:33.480 --> 18:35.000
In those puppet plays,

18:35.080 --> 18:36.320
it only takes a moment.

18:36.400 --> 18:38.600
Why is it taking so long now?

18:38.680 --> 18:40.440
I didn't even kneel this long
for my grandpa.

18:40.520 --> 18:41.920
My legs are completely numb.

18:42.000 --> 18:43.160
Get lost.

18:45.680 --> 18:46.760
My stew…

18:47.280 --> 18:48.880
HALL OF ARMS

18:57.280 --> 19:01.160
Imperial decree!

19:03.160 --> 19:06.200
All soldiers, receive the decree.

19:07.640 --> 19:10.600
"By command of His Majesty.

19:10.680 --> 19:11.840
The rebels of Chongzhou

19:11.920 --> 19:14.200
have thrown the realm into chaos

19:14.280 --> 19:15.320
and oppressed the people.

19:16.040 --> 19:19.680
Governor He Jingyuan of Jizhou
upheld the realm,

19:19.760 --> 19:21.400
slew the rebels,

19:21.480 --> 19:24.960
and fell heroically in battle.

19:25.040 --> 19:27.080
Moved by his loyalty,

19:27.160 --> 19:28.960
His Majesty now posthumously grants him

19:29.040 --> 19:32.840
the title Grand General Kuangzheng.

19:32.920 --> 19:36.320
A state funeral shall be held

19:36.400 --> 19:40.000
to honor his loyalty
and console his spirit.

19:40.080 --> 19:43.440
Let this be proclaimed
throughout the realm so that all may know.

19:44.040 --> 19:48.120
Zhenwei Commandant of Jizhou, Li Huai'an,

19:49.040 --> 19:50.240
rendered great service

19:50.320 --> 19:51.680
in defending the city.

19:51.760 --> 19:54.240
He is hereby appointed
Military Administrator of Jizhou.

19:54.320 --> 19:57.560
Two hundred taels of gold
and 800 taels of silver

19:57.640 --> 20:00.960
are awarded to Li Huai'an and his troops."

20:01.040 --> 20:02.120
We thank His Majesty.

20:11.840 --> 20:15.000
"Jizhou soldier Fan Changyu."

20:18.800 --> 20:19.880
Fan Changyu!

20:21.320 --> 20:22.440
Where did Changyu go?

20:22.520 --> 20:23.680
Fan Changyu!

20:24.280 --> 20:26.160
-I do not know.
-"Fan Changyu.

20:31.400 --> 20:33.320
Jizhou soldier

20:34.400 --> 20:35.560
Fan Changyu,

20:36.360 --> 20:38.640
for slaying Prince Changxin
on the battlefield

20:38.720 --> 20:40.320
and rendering great merit,

20:40.400 --> 20:42.800
is hereby appointed Cavalry Captain,

20:42.880 --> 20:45.240
rank fifth class.

20:45.320 --> 20:48.000
One hundred taels of gold
and 500 taels of silver

20:48.080 --> 20:52.320
-are awarded to Fan Changyu and her men.
-Fifth rank!

20:52.400 --> 20:56.360
As the Jizhou army
cannot remain without leadership,

20:56.440 --> 21:00.600
Military Administrator Li Huai'an
shall take command,

21:00.680 --> 21:04.200
with Cavalry Captain Fan Changyu
serving as his deputy.

21:04.280 --> 21:07.320
Together they shall oversee
the military authority of Jizhou

21:08.120 --> 21:09.480
to steady the army's morale.

21:10.000 --> 21:12.080
Let this decree be proclaimed.

21:12.160 --> 21:14.280
All shall take heed."

21:21.520 --> 21:23.400
Li Huai'an, receive the decree
on her behalf.

21:25.640 --> 21:26.840
We thank His Majesty.

21:29.960 --> 21:32.040
Congratulations,
Military Administrator Li.

21:32.560 --> 21:35.120
Eunuch, you must be tired
from the journey.

21:35.200 --> 21:37.600
If you do not mind,
please stay and rest for a while.

21:37.680 --> 21:39.400
-This way, please.
-Very well.

21:45.120 --> 21:46.280
-Congratulations!
-Congratulations!

21:46.360 --> 21:47.240
Changyu is an official!

21:47.320 --> 21:48.600
-This is fantastic!
-She made it!

21:48.680 --> 21:49.960
Changyu is an official!

21:50.480 --> 21:51.800
-Cavalry Captain!
-Five hundred taels!

21:51.880 --> 21:53.960
I have served in the palace
for so many years,

21:54.040 --> 21:57.440
yet I have never seen
such unruly soldiers.

21:57.520 --> 21:58.560
Those rabble?

21:58.640 --> 22:01.280
How on earth did they manage
to defeat Prince Changxin?

22:04.680 --> 22:06.120
-Captain Fan is over there.
-Come on.

22:06.200 --> 22:07.120
Let's go.

22:08.080 --> 22:09.120
Captain Fan.

22:09.960 --> 22:10.880
Captain Fan.

22:16.080 --> 22:16.920
Captain Fan.

22:17.000 --> 22:19.920
Before, we failed to recognize
your greatness. Forgive our offense.

22:20.000 --> 22:20.840
-Forgive us.
-Forgive us.

22:20.920 --> 22:22.160
What did you just call me?

22:22.240 --> 22:23.720
-Captain Fan.
-Changyu!

22:24.240 --> 22:25.080
Where is she?

22:27.000 --> 22:27.840
Congratulations!

22:27.920 --> 22:28.800
-Congratulations!
-Congratulations!

22:28.880 --> 22:31.560
-You are an official now!
-Official? What kind of official?

22:31.640 --> 22:33.880
Cavalry Captain. An imperial appointment.

22:34.400 --> 22:35.760
-Fifth rank.
-Fifth rank.

22:35.840 --> 22:38.760
Since the dynasty's founding,
no woman has held such rank.

22:38.840 --> 22:39.720
And that's not all.

22:39.800 --> 22:41.120
Even the county magistrate

22:41.200 --> 22:43.720
will have to bow three times
before speaking to you.

22:43.800 --> 22:45.320
Just imagine the prestige.

22:45.400 --> 22:46.240
Really?

22:46.320 --> 22:49.120
-You are truly a woman general now.
-As long as we follow Changyu,

22:49.200 --> 22:51.360
-we will be feasting every day.
-Exactly.

22:51.440 --> 22:52.760
We will want for nothing!

22:52.840 --> 22:55.160
But remember, all of this
is thanks to Changyu.

22:55.240 --> 22:57.040
From today on, I'm no longer Jin Yuanbao.

22:57.120 --> 22:58.720
My new name is Jin Triumph.

22:58.800 --> 23:00.600
The three of them are changing theirs too.

23:00.680 --> 23:01.720
-Man Legion.
-Right.

23:01.800 --> 23:03.000
Man Banner and Man Valor.

23:03.600 --> 23:06.400
That sounds great.
I am treating everyone to stewed meat!

23:09.240 --> 23:11.600
-Come on. Give her a hand.
-Come on.

23:11.680 --> 23:13.440
Sit down. Go sit over there.

23:13.520 --> 23:15.240
All right.

23:15.320 --> 23:16.840
Changyu, let me get you a bowl.

23:16.920 --> 23:19.160
-Triumph, sit here.
-I will pour the wine.

23:19.920 --> 23:20.760
Here.

23:22.760 --> 23:24.120
-Pass it over.
-All right.

23:25.320 --> 23:27.840
-Here.
-Thank you.

23:28.760 --> 23:30.080
-Come on.
-All right.

23:30.160 --> 23:31.480
Not too much. Two big bowls will do.

23:31.560 --> 23:32.400
Take it over.

23:32.480 --> 23:33.440
Here.

23:34.040 --> 23:35.200
Everyone,

23:35.760 --> 23:38.320
-enjoy yourselves.
-That is a generous portion.

23:38.400 --> 23:40.400
-Please enjoy yourselves.
-Bottoms up.

23:40.480 --> 23:41.480
Let me fill your cup.

23:54.960 --> 23:57.000
Administrator Li,
you must be rather disappointed.

23:58.280 --> 23:59.960
You thought that once General He passed,

24:00.560 --> 24:02.240
the military command

24:02.320 --> 24:04.480
would naturally fall
into the Li clan's hands.

24:04.560 --> 24:06.960
Yet in the end, half of it slipped away.

24:09.440 --> 24:11.120
Such a trivial matter
would never disappoint me.

24:12.520 --> 24:13.520
What puzzles me is you.

24:13.600 --> 24:15.920
The military command of Jizhou
is never small.

24:16.000 --> 24:18.160
Why would you entrust it to a young woman

24:18.240 --> 24:20.160
with neither experience nor backing?

24:27.920 --> 24:30.320
Was it not you who filed
for her achievements to the court?

24:31.720 --> 24:33.080
This is simply the outcome.

24:35.760 --> 24:38.480
I credited her merits to protect her.

24:39.360 --> 24:40.800
And I will continue to protect her.

24:44.840 --> 24:48.280
My wife has no need
for protection from an outsider.

24:48.360 --> 24:49.320
Your wife?

24:50.800 --> 24:53.560
If I remember correctly,
Fan Changyu married Yan Zheng,

24:53.640 --> 24:54.560
not you, Xie Zheng.

24:55.080 --> 24:57.720
And even as Yan Zheng,
you two signed a divorce letter.

24:57.800 --> 25:00.320
As things stand,
she has no marriage bond with you at all.

25:00.400 --> 25:03.000
Marquis, why deceive yourself?

25:08.320 --> 25:09.680
Administrator Li, do not forget

25:10.760 --> 25:12.760
your betrothal to the Grand Princess.

25:13.760 --> 25:15.360
A gentleman

25:15.440 --> 25:16.680
doesn't play both sides.

25:35.520 --> 25:37.520
Xie Qi has safely escorted
Yu Qianqian back.

25:37.600 --> 25:39.880
As for Grand Tutor Tao,
he insists on staying.

25:40.600 --> 25:42.920
No matter what we say,
he refuses to return to office.

25:43.000 --> 25:44.720
If he does not go back,

25:45.240 --> 25:47.200
His Majesty may not take kindly to it.

25:47.280 --> 25:48.120
That's no matter.

25:49.840 --> 25:52.640
His Majesty has always been one
to sway with the wind,

25:52.720 --> 25:54.080
clinging to whoever holds power.

25:57.040 --> 25:57.960
There's something else.

25:58.760 --> 26:01.280
The court giving Mrs. Fan
half the military command

26:02.400 --> 26:05.440
is likely the result of the conflict
between Wei Yan and Li Xing.

26:06.400 --> 26:07.480
For years, they've kept

26:08.400 --> 26:09.520
each other in check.

26:10.680 --> 26:12.040
In the end, they simply let go.

26:12.120 --> 26:14.800
To them, Fan Changyu poses no threat.

26:15.480 --> 26:17.040
Better she holds command than I do.

26:19.200 --> 26:21.400
Li Huai'an thought he was being clever,

26:22.320 --> 26:23.880
yet ended up a pawn for both sides.

26:24.840 --> 26:26.360
Those two old foxes.

26:27.320 --> 26:28.880
They are scheming so loudly,

26:29.600 --> 26:31.720
we can hear it all the way in Jizhou.

26:33.560 --> 26:34.600
At this rate,

26:35.280 --> 26:37.160
Fan Changyu is like a child carrying gold

26:37.240 --> 26:38.720
through a bustling market.

26:41.200 --> 26:42.240
Trouble will find her soon.

26:43.640 --> 26:44.840
As long as I am here,

26:46.000 --> 26:47.600
no one will trouble her.

26:49.240 --> 26:50.080
What should we do now?

26:50.760 --> 26:53.000
Split the command in two,
and Mrs. Fan gains nothing.

26:53.080 --> 26:54.600
She'll end up taking the fall.

26:55.240 --> 26:57.040
Grand Tutor Li will surely be displeased.

26:57.120 --> 26:58.640
Grandfather intends to use her

26:58.720 --> 27:00.000
to disrupt Wei Yan's plans.

27:00.080 --> 27:01.920
But it doesn't matter.
We can simply play along.

27:03.680 --> 27:04.680
I can be the one

27:05.240 --> 27:07.240
supporting Fan Changyu too.

27:14.560 --> 27:15.560
Good heavens!

27:16.840 --> 27:18.520
Cavalry Captain.

27:19.280 --> 27:21.800
One hundred taels of gold
and 500 taels of silver!

27:21.880 --> 27:23.160
Ancestors above!

27:23.240 --> 27:26.040
That'll last Fan Changyu
and Fan Changning a lifetime.

27:26.760 --> 27:27.880
That is nothing.

27:27.960 --> 27:31.040
Captain Fan now commands
half the forces of Jizhou.

27:31.560 --> 27:32.960
Xie Qi,

27:33.040 --> 27:34.280
when you return,

27:34.360 --> 27:36.280
please pass a message to Changyu.

27:36.360 --> 27:37.880
Even if she has become a captain,

27:37.960 --> 27:40.640
there's still a saying,
"Don't bite the husband that fed you."

27:41.440 --> 27:43.880
Husband? It's
"Don't bite the hand that fed you."

27:44.520 --> 27:45.400
Stop interrupting.

27:46.080 --> 27:48.160
When Changyu was at her lowest,

27:48.240 --> 27:51.400
it was Yan Zheng who stood by her side.

27:51.480 --> 27:53.520
He was even taken away
by the draft for her sake.

27:53.600 --> 27:55.920
That kind of bond is not ordinary.

27:56.000 --> 27:57.480
Don't let her turn into one

27:57.560 --> 28:00.440
of those women who climb the ladder
and pull it up behind them.

28:00.520 --> 28:01.520
Women? It's normally men who did that.

28:01.600 --> 28:03.440
Why do you keep butting in,

28:03.520 --> 28:05.760
like a water ladle
scooping again and again?

28:05.840 --> 28:09.040
If you say something wrong,
should people not correct you?

28:10.160 --> 28:11.120
Mr. and Mrs. Zhao,

28:11.640 --> 28:12.760
do not worry.

28:12.840 --> 28:14.920
Changyu is not that kind of person.

28:17.640 --> 28:19.320
I will pass your message to Captain Fan

28:19.400 --> 28:20.920
and to our Mar…

28:22.960 --> 28:23.840
our best comrade.

28:25.360 --> 28:27.600
Tell Yan Zheng to stay safe
and come home soon.

28:27.680 --> 28:29.400
A family should all be under one roof.

28:29.480 --> 28:32.240
That is right. All the people of Lin'an
are waiting for him.

28:33.840 --> 28:36.040
Your words will be delivered.

28:37.480 --> 28:40.160
THE SEA OF LEARNING HAS NO END

28:40.760 --> 28:43.280
I never thought Your Highness
would go so far

28:43.360 --> 28:45.000
for Luyuan Academy's headmaster.

28:48.680 --> 28:50.680
It seems our agreement
was also for his sake.

28:53.040 --> 28:55.160
Lingering in Jizhou
instead of returning to the capital…

28:55.680 --> 28:57.480
Got your eye on another man's wife?

28:59.680 --> 29:01.920
Captain Fan's marriage
to Marquis Wu'an was a sham.

29:02.000 --> 29:03.840
She and I are comrades-in-arms.

29:03.920 --> 29:05.080
Nothing improper between us.

29:06.960 --> 29:09.120
Headmaster and I once fought side by side.

29:09.200 --> 29:11.320
Our bond is simply
that of upright comrades.

29:14.720 --> 29:15.760
Captain Fan.

29:19.120 --> 29:22.040
If your intentions are so proper,
why did you panic like that?

29:22.640 --> 29:23.720
You care a lot for a comrade.

29:23.800 --> 29:25.600
Your Highness jests at my expense.

29:29.800 --> 29:32.560
-Mr. Gongsun.
-A joke told twice loses its charm.

29:34.600 --> 29:37.200
I didn't expect Your Highness
and Administrator Li here.

29:38.800 --> 29:40.400
It seems I have intruded.

29:46.800 --> 29:47.640
Wenkan.

29:49.920 --> 29:50.920
I've changed your medicine.

29:51.000 --> 29:52.680
Take it easy and get some rest.

29:54.120 --> 29:56.200
I have a few things to take care of,
so I'll be going now.

29:59.800 --> 30:01.680
Do not move. Count to five.

30:02.200 --> 30:06.480
Five, four, three, two, one.

30:11.040 --> 30:12.320
Your Highness, I…

30:13.000 --> 30:14.280
She does not wish to see you.

30:16.680 --> 30:17.520
Your Highness.

30:18.880 --> 30:19.880
Please wait.

30:20.400 --> 30:21.520
Your Highness.

30:22.040 --> 30:24.560
-Please hear me out.
-Keep your distance from Her Highness!

30:26.800 --> 30:29.280
Your Highness, I just want to say…

30:29.360 --> 30:30.920
-Shut the door.
-Please let me explain.

30:31.000 --> 30:32.040
Your Highness!

30:32.120 --> 30:32.960
Are you leaving?

30:33.560 --> 30:34.440
I am not leaving.

30:35.720 --> 30:36.640
Watch your foot.

30:45.640 --> 30:47.320
-Are you hurt? Let me see.
-No, no.

30:47.840 --> 30:48.920
I am fine.

30:50.320 --> 30:51.280
I am fine.

30:54.560 --> 30:55.400
You lied to me again.

30:58.440 --> 31:00.360
I only wanted to talk to you.

31:01.440 --> 31:03.520
Tell me honestly.
Do you have feelings for Li--

31:03.600 --> 31:04.760
Not in the slightest!

31:05.360 --> 31:06.560
I have no interest in him.

31:06.640 --> 31:07.920
And none in you either.

31:08.600 --> 31:10.240
You came all this way just to ask that?

31:11.880 --> 31:13.240
Is there anything else?

31:20.080 --> 31:21.760
Actually, I…

31:23.520 --> 31:24.840
Headmaster Gongsun,

31:25.920 --> 31:27.640
if you truly have no feelings for me,

31:28.760 --> 31:30.440
then stop coming to see me.

31:42.240 --> 31:45.200
THE SEA OF LEARNING HAS NO END

31:45.800 --> 31:47.120
This foolish mouth…

31:47.200 --> 31:49.400
Why can't I get the words out?

31:54.800 --> 31:55.880
Changyu, go!

32:01.200 --> 32:03.600
Changyu, why are you so distracted today?

32:03.680 --> 32:04.920
Another round?

32:06.960 --> 32:07.800
Come.

32:15.000 --> 32:15.840
Forgive me, Lord Li.

32:18.760 --> 32:19.960
Captain Fan,

32:20.040 --> 32:22.160
I came to discuss something with you.

32:26.920 --> 32:28.240
That live-in husband was bad enough.

32:28.320 --> 32:30.600
This Li Menkan is even worse.

32:33.360 --> 32:34.720
Please come back another day.

32:34.800 --> 32:36.640
I am not in the mood today.

32:38.160 --> 32:41.040
You've been made captain. You must learn
the terrain and military situation.

32:41.840 --> 32:43.600
Everything's marked on the map.
Hope it helps.

32:44.960 --> 32:46.240
If anything is unclear,

32:46.320 --> 32:47.840
I would gladly explain.

32:49.680 --> 32:52.720
Some people love swooping in
when there's an opening.

32:53.400 --> 32:56.520
Looks like that live-in husband
is in trouble.

33:00.720 --> 33:01.800
In that case,

33:02.560 --> 33:03.480
thank you, Lord Li.

33:04.880 --> 33:06.640
If you don't want to be here, leave.

33:07.160 --> 33:09.560
No, no. We cannot leave.

33:09.640 --> 33:10.480
If we left,

33:12.000 --> 33:13.800
who would protect
our captain's reputation?

34:20.400 --> 34:22.040
-Well written!
-Is dinner ready?

34:23.000 --> 34:24.159
That line is great.

34:28.239 --> 34:30.440
It is getting late.
Let's stop here for today.

34:30.960 --> 34:32.440
I've been busy lately.

34:32.960 --> 34:34.760
I may not be able to join you
for a few days.

34:35.360 --> 34:37.239
However, I have invited
the best instructor in Jizhou

34:37.320 --> 34:38.480
to serve as your advisor.

34:38.560 --> 34:40.159
You will soon grow
into the role of captain.

34:41.000 --> 34:42.520
Then thank you, Lord Li.

34:43.040 --> 34:45.960
Among the Enemy Stratagems
is one called "Take the Sheep in Passing".

34:47.199 --> 34:49.159
When an opportunity appears, seize it.

34:49.239 --> 34:52.360
Even the slightest advantage
must not be overlooked.

34:53.159 --> 34:54.400
I know this one.

34:54.480 --> 34:56.480
It means if I see the enemy's sheep,

34:56.560 --> 34:58.960
I grab it and cook myself
a nice pot of mutton soup.

35:00.400 --> 35:01.480
That is… not entirely wrong.

35:02.440 --> 35:04.200
And this one. I know this too.

35:04.280 --> 35:06.000
"Borrow a Knife to Kill."

35:06.080 --> 35:08.960
It means if my weapon
gets knocked away in battle,

35:09.040 --> 35:12.520
I borrow someone else's weapon
and chop the enemy down.

35:12.600 --> 35:14.680
It means you do not have to act yourself.

35:15.200 --> 35:18.160
Instead, you provoke others
to eliminate the enemy for you.

35:18.240 --> 35:20.800
That way, you preserve your own strength.

35:22.760 --> 35:23.600
I see.

35:23.680 --> 35:26.880
I definitely know this one.
"Watch the Fire from Across the River."

35:26.960 --> 35:28.160
Back in my town,

35:28.240 --> 35:31.400
rich families could watch fireworks
from right up close.

35:32.000 --> 35:35.960
But poor kids like us
had to stand far away,

35:36.040 --> 35:39.120
very far away,

35:39.200 --> 35:40.200
to watch them.

35:41.560 --> 35:44.760
It… It is not about fireworks.

35:47.200 --> 35:49.280
It is… Let's move on.

35:51.760 --> 35:54.200
"Point at the Berry and Curse the Ghost."
What does it mean?

35:54.280 --> 35:56.880
It is actually "Point at the Mulberry
and Curse the Locust."

36:03.000 --> 36:04.520
A man of upright character…

36:05.080 --> 36:06.160
-Sir, what is--
-Changyu.

36:07.000 --> 36:07.920
Sir.

36:11.400 --> 36:12.280
How did the lesson go?

36:15.040 --> 36:17.160
Captain Fan is remarkably quick-witted.

36:18.160 --> 36:19.680
One example is all she needs.

36:20.400 --> 36:21.720
A true talent.

36:21.800 --> 36:22.840
You taught well, sir.

36:22.920 --> 36:24.160
Not at all, not at all.

36:25.600 --> 36:27.320
That will be all for today.

36:28.040 --> 36:30.320
-I will take my leave.
-I have learned Sun Zi's Art of War.

36:30.400 --> 36:33.200
Can you teach me some more
from Sun Zi's ancestors tomorrow?

36:34.720 --> 36:35.640
Farewell.

36:36.720 --> 36:37.800
Sir!

36:43.240 --> 36:45.680
Find another teacher as soon as possible.

36:46.840 --> 36:47.680
Understood.

36:48.320 --> 36:49.480
Mr. Liu, thank you for coming.

36:49.560 --> 36:52.480
Every one of my pupils
has become a distinguished general.

36:53.000 --> 36:57.120
You may rest assured.
There is nothing to worry about.

36:58.320 --> 36:59.240
Please.

37:00.440 --> 37:01.400
This way.

37:04.480 --> 37:05.920
HALL OF LETTERS

37:06.000 --> 37:07.360
Mr. Liu, you…

37:07.880 --> 37:09.440
She barely recognizes the characters.

37:09.520 --> 37:11.600
You had better find someone more capable.

37:11.680 --> 37:14.000
-Mr. Liu, please wait.
-I truly cannot teach her.

37:14.080 --> 37:15.000
Farewell.

37:15.080 --> 37:20.160
THE SEA OF LEARNING HAS NO END

37:20.240 --> 37:21.880
-My lord, he--
-Find another.

37:22.640 --> 37:25.560
Please rest assured.
Anyone willing to learn should be taught.

37:26.400 --> 37:27.480
Sir…

37:27.560 --> 37:28.880
-Sir?
-I would rather starve

37:28.960 --> 37:30.520
-than attempt to teach that.
-Wait!

37:30.600 --> 37:32.440
Anyone can be taught.

37:33.560 --> 37:34.960
I am inadequate.

37:35.040 --> 37:36.240
-Please have mercy
-Get up.

37:36.320 --> 37:38.040
-and spare my life!
-Please get up.

37:45.640 --> 37:47.200
‎HALL OF ARMS

37:57.640 --> 38:00.440
SEEKING A KIND, PATIENT, STRONG
MILITARY TUTOR. THREE TAELS FOR TWO HOURS

38:05.360 --> 38:08.040
The student you seek to teach…
Is it Captain Fan?

38:08.120 --> 38:09.040
It is.

38:10.240 --> 38:11.400
Sir!

38:14.320 --> 38:15.560
My lord,

38:15.640 --> 38:17.520
her reputation has spread
throughout the city.

38:17.600 --> 38:18.440
‎JIZHOU PREFECTURAL OFFICE

38:18.520 --> 38:20.560
Three taels an hour, and still no takers.

38:20.640 --> 38:21.560
Forget it.

38:22.320 --> 38:23.680
I will teach her myself.

38:24.640 --> 38:25.480
‎What?

38:26.080 --> 38:31.200
THREE DAYS LATER

38:31.280 --> 38:32.840
What happened?

38:35.160 --> 38:36.400
Captain Fan did this.

38:37.120 --> 38:39.680
Both of you are still injured,
yet you are sparring again?

38:43.200 --> 38:44.240
All internal injuries.

38:46.240 --> 38:47.840
It is getting late.

38:49.000 --> 38:51.360
Help me up. I still need to go teach her.

38:52.800 --> 38:54.040
My lord, please rest.

38:54.560 --> 38:55.640
Stop teaching Captain Fan.

38:55.720 --> 38:58.840
Studying military strategy
must be done step by step. Right?

38:58.920 --> 39:00.480
Studying strategy?

39:01.640 --> 39:02.480
Never thought

39:02.560 --> 39:04.720
teaching could go so wrong.

39:06.480 --> 39:07.680
Lord Li.

39:10.240 --> 39:11.120
Changyu.

39:11.760 --> 39:14.520
Lord Li, no, please. Please stay seated.

39:16.200 --> 39:18.240
Lord Li, I truly owe you an apology.

39:19.600 --> 39:22.320
Perhaps I should just study on my own.

39:23.040 --> 39:26.400
You see, my adoptive father
is quite formidable.

39:26.480 --> 39:28.240
He even wanted to take me as his disciple.

39:28.840 --> 39:31.440
Do you think he is getting old
and his eyesight is failing?

39:32.240 --> 39:34.880
You must possess a rare kind of insight.

39:35.760 --> 39:38.360
Grand Tutor Tao must have seen
that very quality in you.

39:38.960 --> 39:40.520
It is something I cannot compare to.

39:42.040 --> 39:42.880
I think so too.

39:45.120 --> 39:46.480
Maybe I should just

39:46.560 --> 39:47.960
ask him to teach me instead.

39:49.000 --> 39:51.240
Spare the old man. Do not trouble him.

40:20.080 --> 40:22.040
Why can I not get
any of this into my head?

40:23.760 --> 40:25.640
Looks like I am not cut out for studying.

40:43.160 --> 40:46.360
I left some notes in red
between the paragraphs.

40:47.440 --> 40:48.800
Read them when you have time.

41:04.160 --> 41:06.720
When storms darken the sky
The rooster still crows

41:07.240 --> 41:09.560
Having seen the graceful one
How could I not rejoice?

41:10.600 --> 41:12.800
These lines speak

41:12.880 --> 41:14.280
of storm and turmoil, rain pouring,

41:14.800 --> 41:16.360
the world unsettled.

41:17.200 --> 41:19.600
Yet in the midst of all that confusion,

41:20.360 --> 41:21.400
you lift your eyes,

41:22.640 --> 41:23.880
and suddenly, there she is.

41:25.000 --> 41:27.440
Like clouds parting,

41:28.040 --> 41:29.720
a shaft of light falls over you.

41:31.240 --> 41:32.280
Warm. Bright.

41:33.160 --> 41:34.920
And joy rises from somewhere inside.

41:37.480 --> 41:40.240
Why is it that when Yan Zheng teaches me,
I remember everything?

41:48.360 --> 41:50.280
I wonder what he is doing now.

44:31.040 --> 44:34.200
‎NO ANIMALS WERE HARMED
‎IN THE MAKING OF THIS EPISODE

44:34.280 --> 44:35.200
Subtitle translation by: Jiaxin Wang
